Package: spring-boot-app
Version: [[version]]
Section: web
Priority: optional
Architecture: all
Depends: openjdk-11-jre-headless | openjdk-11-jre
Maintainer: DevOps Team <devops@elkanuco.lu>
Description: Spring Boot Demo Application
 A Spring Boot application packaged as a systemd service.
 This package installs the application to /opt/spring-boot-app
 and configures it to run as a systemd service.